               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṭabiba ṭabibān “The Wisest among the Wisest Ones” (fols.
                     2va-23rb)
 II) Malkǝʾa Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq “Image of John the Baptist” (fols.
                     23va-29ra) (ChRep 344, no. 279)
 III) Salām-hymn for John the Baptist
                     (fols. 29ra-29vb) (ChRep 195, no. 70)
 IV) Salām-hymn for John the Baptist
                     (fols. 30va-31rb) (ChRep 195, no. 70)
 V) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of
                     Mary”: 1 miracle (fols. 31va-32rb) (TÄSFA GÄBRÄ ŚǝLLASE (ed.), Taʾammǝra Māryām,
                     Addis Abäba, 1956 A.M, 76-77, no. 21)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
